body:
Minecraft account give away:

Rules to win this giveaway:

1. You must add me on skype (nebbsy.is.a.kid EDIT: If you cannont find my Skype, comment your skype name below) and send me a contact request with your IGN and "I enter" message. If you already have me on skype just send me a PM.

2. If you spam me about the giveaway you will be kicked out.

Things to note about the account:

[+] TID (Transaction ID)
[+] You will receive all information to change account details if you win
[+] No bans on any Minecraft server
[+] Has stats already on Avicus
[+] Changeable name
[+] The account has no forums account on any server
[-] My colorful name history is on the account 

Links for the account: Name mc: https://namemc.com/profile/Pepetheassassin/ec4dcb
Avicus forums (for stats): https://avicus.net/Pepetheassassin#stats

This account will NOT be coming with it's current name. Just holding it for a month for him. The hacking ban is false and just was never removed. 

The give away will happen at 12 PM April 29th 2017 EST. If you do not live in EST you should find out the timezone differences so you can be there for the give away.

The winner will be PM'd on skype upon winning and we will fix the account to their email, security questions and password. 

Good luck, may the odds be ever in your favor.

Check this post frequently as I might change the rules/ giveaway time.
